<chapter id="requirements" xreflabel="Requirements">
<title>Requirements</title>

<para>
The AutoClickChem roll is for use with Rocks &document-version;.
</para>

<para>
You must install the following rolls before installing the AutoClickChem roll:
</para>

<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>
Opal (NOTE: the opal roll requires a reboot)
</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>
Openbabel 
</para></listitem>
</itemizedlist>

<para>
The default Opal roll installation confiures opal to wokr on port 8080. If your opal installation was changed to
wok on a different port you must modify the files /var/www/html/autoclickchem/vars.ini and /var/www/html/autoclickchem/vars.default
</para>

</chapter>

